1.SUMOFSERIES

Program1:
#Series0,2,6,12,	N
n=int(input("Entertherangeofnumber(limit):"))i=1
while(i<=n):print((i*i)-i,end="")
i+=1
Output1:
Entertherangeofnumber(limit):702612203042

