******
Program6:
#Pyramidpattern6
n=int(input("Enterthenumberofrows:"))for iinrange(0,n):
for j in range(0,i+1):print("*",end="")
print("\r")

foriinrange(n,0,-1):
for j in range(0,i-1):print("*",end="")
print("\r")
Output6:
Enterthenumberofrows:5
